Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you might think number three's the weirdest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three. Yamamoto and I had sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, nothing but weird ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you could think up something that weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially that third one... Even if you were just joking, that's just sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It is sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:54.84,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:02:00.80,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:06.93,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:12.90,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:20.28,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:24.99,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:30.92,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:39.80,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:44.72,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:51.85,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:58.61,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:54.84,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:02:00.80,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:06.93,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:12.90,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:20.28,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:24.99,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:30.92,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:39.80,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:44.72,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:51.85,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:58.61,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:13.96,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,950)\fscx112.5\fscy100\pos(159,384)}Episode 12 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been three days since I last spoke to Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto and I had sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Yano was hiding it because he was being kind, not because he was being fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... she's Nana-san's little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you just see Nana-san in her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you also betrayed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, Yano couldn't make a single basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, that's so unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the boys are being tested right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, goddamn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My record of making all five shots since I was in 4th grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to tell when you've got something on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing you're not going to be a pro athlete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, since I'm going to become a romance novelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with your B- essays?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my own story as the plot. I'll have a ton of material.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I a moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a little. You can be unexpectedly clumsy sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess that'd be a compliment for a guy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds a hundred times better than saying you're graceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't really approve of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I call her cellphone, she won't pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't even look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep calling her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already called her fifty times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then call her a hundred times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him I'm asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after he's come all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care! I don't want to see him right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry. Nanami's in the bath right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell him I'm in the bath! Tell him I'm asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I spoke with him now, I'd only be able to say cruel things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... I understand how you feel, but... I think it might be best to leave her alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:06:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes it's easier to talk about things after everyone's calmed down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By tomorrow, I'm sure Nanami will---
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really guarantee that things will be better by tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give those to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What beautiful flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell her "I'll see you tomorrow at school" for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful on your way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't these flowers wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after he came all this way to give you these...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've raised an ogre as a daughter. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Does he really think flowers will make everything better?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would fall for something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you really don't deserve him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man I don't deserve had sex with his ex-girlfriend's little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't the flowers splendid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if his mother went through a lot of effort getting them to grow this beautifully?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all of these roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You big moron...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so dumb...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They smell really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he picked them all from his garden in a rush and wrapped them in a newspaper without thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he really rode a bus carrying this huge bouquet with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could rewrite my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could, I'd do all I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if it would stop you from crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going at this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the bus stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really not fair at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...could've been hurting from it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to tell him off, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...these are the only words that will come from my mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, you big moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I'm too soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not've been able to forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I see his face, I feel like I don't have any choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's frustrating, but I still want to be beside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like they say, you'll always give in to the other when you're in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizu-chin once told me I wouldn't be able to beat someone who's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't change his past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So shouldn't I try to make the present as happy as possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano hates Nana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... hate her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to speak badly of the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I've never even met her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Nana-san's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to make Yano happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must sound pretty dumb, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I warn you of something, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:10:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's just going to be a relationship of hardship and mental agony, you should put an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we go on Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how about the zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I suggested the zoo before, you made fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go see the monkeys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in the mood for monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are you in the mood for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls really love the beach, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know of a beach near here that's not like the ones you see in pictures. Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If people could do things over, I wonder if they...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would choose a different path to walk down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check out this kelp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would they choose the people they encounter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and choose the things that made them happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea's shining... it's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad we came?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. I'm glad. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could probably do it over there if we used that as a bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they only picked the things that made them happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...how wonderful life would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's collect seashells!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a jar with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the pretty-looking ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? That one isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do after collecting these?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make them into a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, can I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see your panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any cherry petal shells, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry petal shells?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the pink ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think we'd have to go a little further south to find nice ones like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tickled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "how"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, it's just a sea slater!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:56.75,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't bite. Don't wor--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! A bug! Over here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross, gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back! Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I made too much of a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hate bugs, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just surprised me a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you... confusing me with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forget about...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Nana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-san's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She lied to you, betrayed you, and left you all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes sense for you to get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right to hold a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must want to complain to her, but you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Nana-san's dead! She's no longer here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me here, now, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you've wanted to say. All about your grudge, or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing like that left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be something you've wanted to say to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shush already. There's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It pisses me off."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You big idiot."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Drop dead."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen to everything you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Nana-san were here, what would you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Nana-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys are in the same class as Yuri, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but could you lend me some cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left without paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They call that sort of thing "being blind".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't really fallen in love with anyone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They call people like you "immature know-it-alls".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and really fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still think he's gonna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you waiting around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To gather my rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a hand warmer. It's a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... what do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Figure out your own problems yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a moron, I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell you, but in exchange, you better do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it make me happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably something where no one cries or gets yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where no one gets hit or has stuff thrown at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... why don't we both go searching for our own happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you saw her now, what would you tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what you're feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're saying and what you're doing are contradictory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I won't betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you absolutely won't betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I hate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the woman I loved so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forgive you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please... I want you to come back to me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to make Yano happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... we need to make my past pale in comparison to our present.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear it on the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a shooting star, I wish to be with Nana-chan forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for not being able to keep our promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano made his wish long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless he hated her... Yano seems like he'd be crushed by all of the sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was his way to protect himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me that you'll never leave my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why people... make promises they won't be able to keep...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who betrayed who?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said "serves you right" before as well, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-san's pretty gutless, huh? I didn't expect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.32,0:22:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to comfort you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'll ever fall for that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:22:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was dreaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...happy dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:14.13,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisetsu ga sukoshi ugoita ki ga suru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:22.56,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hizashi mo mijikaku itsukazurete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:30.94,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Futari no basu ha kawaranai machi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:34.90,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashitteiru koto...
