Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:44.92,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro wo fukaku somete yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:51.34,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitto saigo no jikan da to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:58.39,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Namida koraeteta
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:04.86,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Omoide nante itsumo kanashisugiru bakari
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:11.70,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Isso wasurete shimaitai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:18.24,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nido to aenai kimi senaka to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:24.50,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Saigo no yuuhi mitsumetsudzuketa
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:31.05,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsumo itsumo yasashisugita ne
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:39.93,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima wa ososugiru keredo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:48.65,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the sunset kimi wo ushinaitakunai
