Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:56.91,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mou ai no hibi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.91,0:24:03.04,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mou kaeranai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:09.34,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mou ai no hibi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:15.56,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mou kaeranai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.56,0:24:24.36,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Subete ha yume no naka sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:14.13,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like the seasons have changed slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:22.56,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and the sunbeams have thinned and will one day shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:30.94,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was relieved, knowing our bus
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:34.90,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,was riding through...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:39.71,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The sunset stretches my shadow long and thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:44.92,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Its colors deeply dye my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:51.34,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,When you said this was probably the last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:58.39,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I held back my tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:04.86,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories are always too sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:11.70,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to forget them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:18.24,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I continued to watch the last sunset
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:24.50,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and your back that I would never see again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:31.05,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,You were always too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:39.93,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,And even though it's too late now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:48.65,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the sunset. I don't want to lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:55.28,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sky enveloping me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:17:02.46,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,your face would always look down at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:10.67,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it so the sun never sets...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:24.89,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The room we always lived in, that photograph when we walked on the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:38.32,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The promise we made will go unkept.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:51.71,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs31}I became so lonely alone in my room, listening to the distant rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:53.59,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,One day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:44.84,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt as if I heard you calling out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:57.02,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Without thinking, I looked around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:21:02.49,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just the wind pulling a prank on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:09.45,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one on the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:15.92,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky's the same color
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:22.05,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,as on the day when we broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:27.39,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, the seasons will change again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:33.60,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though flowers are blooming on the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:39.94,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those days of love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:46.11,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,will never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:50.74,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a dream now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:33.58,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The bright sunbeams glint off the distant houses and stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:39.50,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,My small things are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:43.96,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,already crossing over the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:51.43,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a gentle city,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:58.56,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, it's painful to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:23:04.78,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were both in love with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:11.07,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,it was just too beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:16.33,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those days still live on in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:22.63,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know what to do from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:28.93,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those days of love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.93,0:23:35.10,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,will never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.10,0:23:40.35,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a dream now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:56.91,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those days of love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.91,0:24:03.04,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,will never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:09.34,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those days of love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:15.56,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,will never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.56,0:24:24.36,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a dream now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.95,0:25:34.97,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDC6CE3&\c&HFDE2FF&\fscx105\fscy122.5\pos(434,377)}Episode 13 Preview...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.31,0:25:08.32,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I regret what I did\N so much that I want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.32,0:25:11.57,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then... back at that place... \Nthose actions I took...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.57,0:25:14.32,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I choose\N is always wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.91,0:25:16.57,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want you to listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.57,0:25:17.49,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.08,0:25:19.45,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.16,0:25:23.21,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,What I told you this\N morning was my final notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.29,0:25:27.29,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you\N that you'd regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.29,0:25:28.38,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.38,0:25:32.51,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold back anymore!
